{"tid":1729404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「極重要」 Times投票 即棄Email都投得","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:10:00.000Z","uid":65449,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4fca3ec3d81e14f04e4d465940ebd8fd1642a8","tid":1729404,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">#巴打報料 #尖沙咀 <br />\n小心速龍<br />\n在科學館走各火通路出口走出來捉人<br />\n貼近理大公共防煙門也要小心也可能有速龍出來<br />\n<br />\n另<br />\n有速龍埋伏香港歷史博物館內❗️<br />\n有速龍埋伏香港歷史博物館內❗️<br />\n有速龍埋伏香港歷史博物館內❗️<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n注意兩架銳武 水炮車可能做煙幕<br />\n隨時會用銳武衝 後面速龍再衝出黎咬人<br />\n‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足小心裝甲車 側窗 水平射tg冷槍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Times</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=2ca997fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即棄Email都受 <br />\n投票洗撚爆佢<br />\n上呀鍵盤戰士</span></span>"},{"pid":"a30288a0e055c7229127cf2a43ee4ab596aeb860","tid":1729404,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"覺推"},{"pid":"7d592efda58c2939a5e72c8390a68797d88eff10","tid":1729404,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"警察砲轟poly，要推畀國際知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 組不斷更新 Task3</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=a447df25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n撳 <span style=